drade ... 2004\"/>\n|\n|-\n!Serbia\n|12,706<ref name=\"census_rs\">{{cite web |url = http://webrzs.stat.gov.rs/WebSite/Public/ReportResultView.aspx?rptId=3690 |title = 2011 Census \u2013 Mother tongue |accessdate = 2015-01-20 |archive-url = https://archive.today/20141023154939/http://webrzs.stat.gov.rs/WebSite/Public/ReportResultView.aspx?rptId=3690 |archive-date = 2014-10-23 |url-status = dead }}</ref>\n|12,706<ref name=\"census_rs\" />\n|\n|-\n!Rest of the Balkans\n|\n|15,807<ref name=\"hr-census\">{{Croatian Census 2011|E}}</ref><ref name=\"2005 census\">{{cite web |url=http://www.uni-koeln.de/jur-fak/ostrecht/minderheitenschutz/Vortraege/BiH/BiH_Marko_Railic.pdf |title=2005 census |format=PDF |language=de |accessdate=2014-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303183909/http://www.uni-koeln.de/jur-fak/ostrecht/minderheitenschutz/Vortraege/BiH/BiH_Marko_Railic.pdf |archive-date=2016-03-03 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=\"2003 Census\">[http://www.monstat.org/Popis/Popis01a.zip 2003 Census]{{Dead link|date=August 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stat.si/popis2002/si/rezultati/rezultati_red.asp?ter=SLO&st=7 |title=Statisti\u010dni urad RS \u2013 Popis 2002 |publisher=Stat.si |date= |accessdate=2014-08-07}}</ref>\n|25,000\n|-\n!Canada\n|18,440<ref name=\"census_ca\">{{cite web|url=http://www12.statcan.gc.ca/census-recensement/2006/dp-pd/tbt/Rp-eng.cfm?TABID=1&LANG=E&APATH=3&DETAIL=0&DIM=0&FL=A&FREE=0&GC=0&GK=0&GRP=1&PID=89272&PRID=0&PTYPE=88971,97154&S=0&SHOWALL=0&SUB=0&Temporal=2006&THEME=70&VID=0&VNAMEE=&VNAMEF= |title=2006 Census \u2013 Language spoken most often at home |publisher=2.statcan.gc.ca |date= |accessdate=2014-08-07}}</ref>\n|18,440<ref name=\"census_ca\" />\n|150,000<ref name=\"autogenerated1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.mfa.gov.mk/ |title=Estimate from the MFA |accessdate=2005-10-27 |url-status=bot: unknown |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080530070621/http://www.mfa.gov.mk//Upload/ContentManagement/Files/Broj%20na%