{"title_page": "Till Kraemer", "text_new": "{{autobiography|date=May 2011}}\n{{Infobox adult biography\n| name            = Till Kraemer\n| image           = Till Kraemer.jpg\n| caption         =\n| birth_name      =\n| birth_date      = {{birth date and age|1977|08|18}}\n| birth_place     = [[Bad Godesberg]], [[West Germany]]\n| death_date      =\n| de ath_place     =\n| spouse          =\n| height          = {{height|m=1.80}}\n| weight          =\n| alias           =\n| number_of_films = 125<ref name=\"bild.de\">[http://www.bild.de/unterhaltung/erotik/erotik/sexstar-till-kraemer-gruendet-geile-enzyklopaedie-11519474.bild.html Pornopedia: Sexstar Till Kraemer (32) gr\u00fcndet geile Enzyklop\u00e4die], ''[[Bild]]'', February 18, 2010</ref>\n| website         = {{URL|till-kraemer.com}}\n}}\n\n'''Till Kraemer''' (born August 18, 1977) is a [[Germany|German]] [[actor]], former [[pornographic actor]], [[columnist]], [[Television presenter|television host]], [[Trance (music genre)|trance]] [[Disc jockey|DJ]], [[Film criticism|film critic]] and stand-up comedian.<ref>Vom Pornostar zum Comedian, [[Hamburger Morgenpost]], December 31, 2018</ref><ref>[https://www.mopo.de/hamburg/pornostar-packt-aus-so-wild-geht-es-zu--wenn-die-kameras-aus-sind-31808288 Pornostar packt aus: So wild geht es zu, wenn die Kameras aus sind], Mopo.de, January 20, 2019</ref><ref>[https://www.mopo.de/hamburg/pornostar-packt-aus-so-viel-geld-gibt-s-pro-sex-dreh---und-das-war-meine-groesste-panne-31923224 Pornostar packt aus: So viel Geld gibt's pro Sex-Dreh \u2013 und das war meine gr\u00f6\u00dfte Panne], Mopo.de, January 23, 2019</ref><ref>[https://www.mopo.de/hamburg/pornostar-packt-aus-das-passierte-bei-meinem-schlimmsten-sex-dreh-31943820 Pornostar packt aus: Das passierte bei meinem schlimmsten Sex-Dreh], Mopo.de, January 27, 2019</ref><ref>[http://www.hamburger-wochenblatt.de/langenhorn/kultur/ella-comedy-club-mix-show-d16542.html ella Comedy Club: Mix Show], Hamburger Wochenblatt, April 25, 2014</ref><ref>[http://www.hamburger-wochenblatt.de/eppendorf/kultur/stand-up-comedy-benefizabend-trusheims-comedy-club-im-music-club-live-d18435.html Stand Up Comedy Benefizabend - Trusheims Comedy Club im Music Club Live], Hamburger Wochenblatt, August 22, 2014</ref> He runs [[Pornopedia]], an online encyclopedia about [[pornography]], [[erotica]], and sexuality.<ref name=\"bild.de\"/>\n\n==Life==\nKraemer grew up in the [[Grafschaft, Rhineland|Grafschaft]], a [[Municipalities of Germany|municipality]] in the district of [[Ahrweiler (district)|Ahrweiler]] in [[Rhineland-Palatinate]], and he started his career as an actor. He appeared as a [[supporting actor]] on television shows such as ''[[Die Rettungsflieger]]'' and ''[[Tatort]]''. To earn a living, Kraemer also began to work as a [[porn actor]] for the German studio Inflagranti Film Berlin in 2005.<ref>[http://www.sat1.de/ratgeber_magazine/akte/topthemen/erotisch/content/11989/ \u201eEndstation Pornofilm: Wenn M\u00e4nner keine Arbeit finden\u201c], Akte 06, June 1, 2006</ref> In 2006 and 2007, he did his own porn series ''Mach\u2019s mit Till'' (\"Drill with Till\") for the [[Bremen]]-based studio SD Evolution Video.<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20100524171125/http://www.bremen4u.de/meetandflirt/flirt_area/serien/jobs/schauspieler.jsp \u201eGeschafft, ich bin Porno-Star!\u201c], bremen4u</ref> During that time, Kraemer was nominated for three erotic awards. After 125 movies,<ref name=\"bild.de\"/> Kraemer ended his career as a porn actor in December 2007<ref>[http://de.till-kraemer.com/presse/Titelstory4.pdf \u201eDer perfekte Blowjob\u201c], St. Pauli Nachrichten \u2013 Das Kiez-Magazin, issue 03/2009, June 18, 2009</ref> due to the job related health risks.<ref>[http://de.till-kraemer.com/presse/pressespiegel/jolie/images/004.jpg Mein Freund ist ein Pornostar], ''[[Jolie (magazine)|Jolie]]'', January 31, 2009</ref>\n\nIn 2006, Kraemer performed in the Schn\u00fcrschuh-Theater in Bremen. He portrayed Jake